== Overview ==

Dragon Quest III for SNES features extensive item lists including weapons, armor, and consumables for all classes. This page documents all items.

== Item Data Structure ==

Each item entry is 12 bytes:

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Offset !! Size !! Description
|-
| $00 || 1 || Item ID
|-
| $01 || 1 || Item type
|-
| $02 || 1 || Effect value
|-
| $03 || 1 || Equip flags (class mask)
|-
| $04-$05 || 2 || Buy price
|-
| $06-$07 || 2 || Sell price
|-
| $08-$0B || 4 || Special effects, description
|}

